===Etymology===
From {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|surrepticius||stolen, furtive, clandestine|lang=la}}, from ''[[surreptus]]'', past participle of ''[[surripere]]'' ("seize secretly, steal, pilfer"), from ''[[sub-]]'' ("under") + ''[[rapere]]'' ("to snatch").

